Date:   Sun Dec 2 22:40:16 2018 +0100

    Feat/ffquip (#9)
    
    A fully pythonic FFQUIP which gives access to arbitrary interaction potentials that are implemented in QUIP. Requires ASE and QUIPPY.
    
    * added an example for OH morse potential
    
    * Passes QUIP parameters as separate fields, updated the examples.
    
    * uses the unit conversion defined in i-pi to change between internal and QUIP units. Also defined a new one for forces.

